{"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/ActionGroupProtocol"]]},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/ActionGroupProtocol\/activateAction(actionName:parameter:)-3g8ic","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"GIO"}],"externalID":"s:3GIO19ActionGroupProtocolPAAE08activateB010actionName9parameterySPys4Int8VGSg_4GLib10VariantRefVSgtF","roleHeading":"Instance Method","extendedModule":"GIO","symbolKind":"method","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"activateAction"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"actionName"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:SP","text":"UnsafePointer"},{"text":"<","kind":"text"},{"text":"gchar","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:gtypes.h@T@gchar"},{"kind":"text","text":">!, "},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"parameter"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:4GLib10VariantRefV","text":"VariantRef"},{"text":"?)","kind":"text"}],"title":"activateAction(actionName:parameter:)"},"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Activate the named action within "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"actionGroup"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"activateAction","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"actionName","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"text":"UnsafePointer","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:SP"},{"kind":"text","text":"<"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"gchar","preciseIdentifier":"c:gtypes.h@T@gchar"},{"text":">!, ","kind":"text"},{"text":"parameter","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:4GLib10VariantRefV","text":"VariantRef","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":"? = nil)","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If the action is expecting a parameter, then the correct type of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"parameter must be given as "},{"code":"parameter","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":".  If the action is expecting no"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"parameters then "},{"code":"parameter","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" must be "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NULL"},{"type":"text","text":".  See"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"[method"},{"code":"Gio.ActionGroup.get_action_parameter_type","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"]."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If the [type"},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/ActionGroup"},{"text":"] implementation supports asynchronous remote","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"activation over D-Bus, this call may return before the relevant"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"D-Bus traffic has been sent, or any replies have been received. In"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"order to block on such asynchronous activation calls,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"[method"},{"code":"Gio.DBusConnection.flush","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"] should be called prior to the code, which"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"depends on the result of the action activation. Without flushing"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the D-Bus connection, there is no guarantee that the action would"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"have been activated."}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The following code which runs in a remote app instance, shows an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"example of a ‘quit’ action being activated on the primary app","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"instance over D-Bus. Here [method"},{"code":"Gio.DBusConnection.flush","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":"] is called","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"before ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"exit()"},{"type":"text","text":". Without "},{"code":"g_dbus_connection_flush()","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", the ‘quit’ action"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"may fail to be activated on the primary instance."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["\/\/ call ‘quit’ action on primary instance","g_action_group_activate_action (G_ACTION_GROUP (app), \"quit\", NULL);","","\/\/ make sure the action is activated now","g_dbus_connection_flush (…);","","g_debug (\"Application has been terminated. Exiting.\");","","exit (0);"],"syntax":"c","type":"codeListing"}]}],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"minor":3,"major":0},"sections":[],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/gio\/actiongroupprotocol\/activateaction(actionname:parameter:)-3g8ic"]}],"references":{"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO":{"type":"topic","abstract":[],"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO","title":"GIO","url":"\/documentation\/gio","role":"collection","kind":"symbol"},"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO/ActionGroupProtocol":{"role":"symbol","title":"ActionGroupProtocol","abstract":[{"code":"GActionGroup","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" represents a group of actions."}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"ActionGroupProtocol","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/gio\/actiongroupprotocol","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/ActionGroupProtocol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"protocol"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"ActionGroupProtocol","kind":"identifier"}]},"d